Our first take on swimwear featuring our summer print, Harbour. Designed to be your most versatile summer staple made from smooth, stretchy fabric — can be worn as-is or paired with bottoms, as seen here with our Asymmetrical Cotton Skirt. Best for those who are comfortable without in-built support; no padding or underwire included. Comes fully lined.

Print placement is fixed for each piece, except for the straps. 

Claire (orange print) is a regular S and wearing a size XS here.
Elaina (blue print) is a regular S and wearing a size S here.

This item is not eligible for any exchanges or returns.
